<% content_for :title, "Terms of Service" %>

<div class="zone--dark bg-db-bg min-h-screen pt-16">
  <%# ── Page Header ── %>
  <header class="border-b border-db-border">
    <div class="page-prose text-center">
      <p class="font-mono text-db-accent text-xs tracking-widest uppercase mb-4">Legal</p>
      <h1 class="text-db-text font-bold tracking-tight leading-tight
                 text-[clamp(2.4rem,5vw,4rem)]">
        Terms of Service
      </h1>
      <p class="font-mono text-db-muted text-xs tracking-widest mt-4">
        Last updated: April 2025
      </p>
    </div>
  </header>

  <%# ── Body ── %>
  <div class="page-prose">

    <div class="prose-db">

      <section class="mb-14">
        <p class="font-mono text-db-muted text-sm leading-relaxed tracking-wide">
          These Terms of Service ("Terms") govern your use of the Death Bloom Coffee Roasters website
          and any purchases you make through it. By accessing our site or placing an order, you agree
          to be bound by these Terms. Death Bloom Coffee Roasters, LLC ("Death Bloom," "we," "us," "our")
          is a specialty coffee roaster headquartered in Denver, Colorado.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-14">
        <h2 class="section-heading">Use of the Site</h2>
        <p class="font-mono text-db-muted text-sm leading-relaxed tracking-wide mb-4">
          You must be at least 18 years old to create an account or place an order. By using the site, you confirm
          that you meet this requirement. You agree not to:
        </p>
        <ul class="policy-list">
          <li>Use the site for any unlawful purpose or in violation of these Terms.</li>
          <li>Attempt to gain unauthorized access to any part of the site or its infrastructure.</li>
          <li>Scrape, crawl, or harvest data from the site without our written consent.</li>
          <li>Interfere with or disrupt the operation of the site or its servers.</li>
          <li>Impersonate another person or misrepresent your affiliation with any entity.</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="font-mono text-db-muted text-sm leading-relaxed tracking-wide mt-4">
          We reserve the right to suspend or terminate access for any user who violates these Terms.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-14">
        <h2 class="section-heading">Orders and Payment</h2>
        <h3 class="subsection-heading">Placing an order</h3>
        <p class="font-mono text-db-muted text-sm leading-relaxed tracking-wide">
          All orders are subject to acceptance and product availability. We roast to order in small batches —
          listed roast dates and ship times are estimates. We will notify you if a product is unavailable or
          if your order cannot be fulfilled.
        </p>

        <h3 class="subsection-heading">Pricing</h3>
        <p class="font-mono text-db-muted text-sm leading-relaxed tracking-wide">
          All prices are displayed in USD and are subject to change without notice. Applicable sales tax
          will be calculated and displayed at checkout. We reserve the right to correct pricing errors,
          and we will notify you before charging a corrected amount.
        </p>

        <h3 class="subsection-heading">Payment</h3>
        <p class="font-mono text-db-muted text-sm leading-relaxed tracking-wide">
          Payments are processed securely by Stripe. By placing an order, you authorize us to charge the
          payment method on file for the total amount. We do not store your payment card information on our
          servers.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-14">
        <h2 class="section-heading">Shipping and Delivery</h2>
        <p class="font-mono text-db-muted text-sm leading-relaxed tracking-wide">
          We ship within the United States. Shipping costs are calculated at checkout based on destination
          and selected shipping method. Estimated delivery times are provided by the carrier and are not
          guaranteed. Death Bloom is not responsible for carrier delays, lost packages, or delivery failures
          due to an incorrect address provided at checkout.
        </p>
        <p class="font-mono text-db-muted text-sm leading-relaxed tracking-wide mt-4">
          Risk of loss and title for products purchased from Death Bloom passes to you upon delivery to the
          carrier.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-14">
        <h2 class="section-heading">Returns and Refunds</h2>
        <p class="font-mono text-db-muted text-sm leading-relaxed tracking-wide">
          Because coffee is a perishable, consumable product roasted fresh to order, we do not accept returns.
          If your order arrives damaged, is incorrect, or has a quality defect, contact us within 7 days of
          delivery at <span class="text-db-text"><%= support_email %></span> with your order number and
          a photo of the issue. We will make it right — either by reshipping or issuing a refund at our discretion.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-14">
        <h2 class="section-heading">Accounts</h2>
        <p class="font-mono text-db-muted text-sm leading-relaxed tracking-wide">
          You are responsible for maintaining the confidentiality of your account credentials and for all
          activity that occurs under your account. Notify us immediately at
          <span class="text-db-text"><%= support_email %></span> if you suspect unauthorized access.
          We reserve the right to terminate accounts that violate these Terms or remain inactive for extended
          periods.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-14">
        <h2 class="section-heading">Intellectual Property</h2>
        <p class="font-mono text-db-muted text-sm leading-relaxed tracking-wide">
          All content on this site — including the Death Bloom name, logos, wordmark, photography, copy, and
          design — is the property of Death Bloom Coffee Roasters, LLC and is protected by U.S. copyright,
          trademark, and other intellectual property laws. You may not reproduce, distribute, or create
          derivative works from our content without our written permission.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-14">
        <h2 class="section-heading">Disclaimer of Warranties</h2>
        <p class="font-mono text-db-muted text-sm leading-relaxed tracking-wide">
          The site and its contents are provided "as is" without warranties of any kind, express or implied,
          including but not limited to implied warranties of merchantability, fitness for a particular purpose,
          and non-infringement. We do not warrant that the site will be uninterrupted, error-free, or free of
          viruses or other harmful components.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-14">
        <h2 class="section-heading">Limitation of Liability</h2>
        <p class="font-mono text-db-muted text-sm leading-relaxed tracking-wide">
          To the maximum extent permitted by law, Death Bloom Coffee Roasters, LLC and its members, employees,
          and agents will not be liable for any indirect, incidental, special, consequential, or punitive
          damages arising out of or related to your use of the site or purchase of products, even if advised
          of the possibility of such damages. Our total liability for any claim arising from a purchase will
          not exceed the amount you paid for the product in question.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-14">
        <h2 class="section-heading">Governing Law</h2>
        <p class="font-mono text-db-muted text-sm leading-relaxed tracking-wide">
          These Terms are governed by the laws of the State of Colorado, without regard to conflict of law
          principles. Any disputes arising under these Terms will be resolved exclusively in the state or
          federal courts located in Denver, Colorado.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-14">
        <h2 class="section-heading">Changes to These Terms</h2>
        <p class="font-mono text-db-muted text-sm leading-relaxed tracking-wide">
          We may update these Terms from time to time. We will post the revised Terms with an updated date.
          Your continued use of the site after changes are posted constitutes your acceptance of the revised
          Terms. We encourage you to review this page periodically.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-14">
        <h2 class="section-heading">Contact</h2>
        <p class="font-mono text-db-muted text-sm leading-relaxed tracking-wide">
          Questions about these Terms? Reach us at:<br><br>
          Death Bloom Coffee Roasters, LLC<br>
          Denver, Colorado<br>
          <span class="text-db-text"><%= support_email %></span>
        </p>
      </section>

    </div>

    <div class="mt-16 pt-12 border-t border-db-border flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-6 sm:gap-10">
      <%= link_to "← Back to Home", root_path,
            class: "font-mono text-db-muted text-xs tracking-widest uppercase hover:text-db-text transition-colors duration-150" %>
      <%= link_to "Privacy Policy →", privacy_policy_path,
            class: "font-mono text-db-muted text-xs tracking-widest uppercase hover:text-db-text transition-colors duration-150" %>
    </div>

  </div>
</div>
